title: How Successful People Think
itunes:title: How Successful People Think
description:
Episode 433 - There is no background, sex, parental requirement, or ethnicity required for success, success starts in the mind and ends in the physical world. Therefore, in this episode I teach the 3 things that successful people think about differently and how you can change your mind to match theirs.
